summary: Xena warrior princess 1h war axe and shield
descriptionHtml:
I\'m So bad at back stories but here we go Xena is Lydia\'s long lost sister hence Lydia mother abandon her and her father around the time of the Great war.  The Rumors of a housecarl named Lydia reach her so she started making her way towards Whiterun.   As fate would have it, She became broke around Riverwood and started a cleaning job for the General Store owner.  After visiting Whiterun and finding out Lydia was out with the Thane, she continued her job and started staying at the Sleeping Giants Inn.

Well let me see requires Apachiiskyhair.  I think she a bit overpower well her shield and axe are.

Enjoy hope yall like it
author: OZZY
